<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">See also: <a href="/wiki/Black_people_and_Mormonism" title="Black people and Mormonism">Black people and Mormonism</a>, <a href="/wiki/Native_American_people_and_Mormonism" title="Native American people and Mormonism">Native American people and Mormonism</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Interracial_marriage_and_the_LDS_Church" class="mw-redirect" title="Interracial marriage and the LDS Church">Interracial marriage and the LDS Church</a></div>
