<div class="sidebar-list mw-collapsible mw-collapsed"><div class="sidebar-list-title"><a href="/wiki/Origin_of_the_Book_of_Mormon" title="Origin of the Book of Mormon">Origin</a></div><div class="sidebar-list-content mw-collapsible-content"><div class="hlist">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Cumorah" title="Cumorah">Cumorah</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Golden_plates" title="Golden plates">Golden plates</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Joseph_Smith" title="Joseph Smith">Joseph Smith</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Emma_Smith" title="Emma Smith">Emma Smith</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Oliver_Cowdery" title="Oliver Cowdery">Oliver Cowdery</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Sidney_Rigdon" title="Sidney Rigdon">Sidney Rigdon</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/David_Whitmer" title="David Whitmer">David Whitmer</a></li>
