<li><a href="/wiki/Lucy_Harris" title="Lucy Harris">Lucy Harris</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Book_of_Mormon_witnesses" title="Book of Mormon witnesses">Book of Mormon witnesses</a>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Three_Witnesses" title="Three Witnesses">Three Witnesses</a></li>
