<li id="cite_note-Balmer-4"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Balmer_4-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Balmer_4-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBalmerRiess2015" class="citation book cs1">Balmer, Randall; <a href="/wiki/Jana_Riess" title="Jana Riess">Riess, Jana</a> (December 8, 2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=mQ7TCgAAQBAJ"><i>Mormonism and American Politics</i></a>. Columbia University Press. p.&#160;168. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-231-54089-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-231-54089-6"><bdi>978-0-231-54089-6</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Mormonism+and+American+Politics&amp;rft.pages=168&amp;rft.pub=Columbia+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2015-12-08&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-231-54089-6&amp;rft.aulast=Balmer&amp;rft.aufirst=Randall&amp;rft.au=Riess%2C+Jana&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DmQ7TCgAAQBAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+teachings+on+skin+color" class="Z3988"></span></span>
