<li id="cite_note-23"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBowman2012" class="citation book cs1">Bowman, Matthew (2012). <span class="id-lock-registration" title="Free registration required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/mormonpeoplemaki00bowm_0/page/176"><i>The Mormon People</i></a></span>. <a href="/wiki/Random_House" title="Random House">Random House</a>. p.&#160;176. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780679644903" title="Special:BookSources/9780679644903"><bdi>9780679644903</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Internet_Archive" title="Internet Archive">Internet Archive</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Mormon+People&amp;rft.pages=176&amp;rft.pub=Random+House&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.isbn=9780679644903&amp;rft.aulast=Bowman&amp;rft.aufirst=Matthew&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fmormonpeoplemaki00bowm_0%2Fpage%2F176&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+teachings+on+skin+color" class="Z3988"></span></span>
