<li id="cite_note-47"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-47">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFKimball1960" class="citation magazine cs1"><a href="/wiki/Spencer_W._Kimball" title="Spencer W. Kimball">Kimball, Spencer</a> (December 1960). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/improvementera6312unse/page/n52/mode/1up">"The Day of the Lamanites"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Improvement_Era" title="Improvement Era">Improvement Era</a></i>. Salt Lake City: <a href="/wiki/LDS_Church" class="mw-redirect" title="LDS Church">LDS Church</a>. p.&#160;923.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Improvement+Era&amp;rft.atitle=The+Day+of+the+Lamanites&amp;rft.pages=923&amp;rft.date=1960-12&amp;rft.aulast=Kimball&amp;rft.aufirst=Spencer&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fimprovementera6312unse%2Fpage%2Fn52%2Fmode%2F1up&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+teachings+on+skin+color" class="Z3988"></span></span>
